panels.description: The amount of bytes read from the Alluxio file system
panels.title: Bytes Served from Alluxio

panels.description: Displays the current amount of open connections in Alluxio
panels.title: Total Open Connections

panels.description: The total amount of UFSes mounted in the Alluxio file system by taking the difference of mount and unmount operations
panels.title: UFSes Mounted

panels.description: The amount of bytes read from the UFSes
panels.title: Bytes Served from UFS

panels.description: Displays the percentage of free Alluxio storage with thresholds from 100-50%, 50-10%, and 10-0%
panels.title: % Free Alluxio Space

panels.description: Displays the overall cluster activity by taking the average rate of operation calls across all Alluxio operations
panels.title: Cluster Activity

panels.description:
Displays the 50th, 95th, and 99th percentiles call time for the getFileInfo metadata operation.
(Labelled as GetStatus in code)
panels.title: Get File Info Operation

panels.description: Displays the 50th, 95th, and 99th percentiles call time for the CreateFile metadata operation.
panels.title: Create File Operation

panels.description: Displays the 50th, 95th, and 99th percentiles call time for the getConfiguration metadata operation.
panels.title: Get Configuration Operation

panels.description:
Displays the 50th, 95th, and 99th percentiles call time for the blockHeartbeat metadata operation.

Note: This is not a graph for the actual Block Heartbeat just how long it took the operation to run
panels.title: Block Heartbeat Operation

panels.description:
Displays the 50th, 95th, and 99th percentiles call time for the workerHeartbeat metadata operation.

Note: This is not a graph for the actual Worker Heartbeat just how long it took the operation to run
panels.title: Worker Heartbeat Operation

panels.description: Displays the current number of how many directories Alluxio has created since starting
panels.title: Directories Created

panels.description: displays the number of times the FileInfosGot operation was called
panels.title: File Infos Got

panels.description: Displays the total paths located in the Alluxio file system
panels.title: Total Paths

panels.description: Displays how many times the CompleteFile operation has been called
panels.title: Complete File Operations

panels.description: Displays the amount of directories that Alluxio has created (Not the current amount of directories)
panels.title: Create Directory Oprtations

panels.description: Displays how many times the deletePath operation has been called (And how many total paths have been deleted)
panels.title: Delete Path Operations

panels.description: Displays the current number of pinned files in Alluxio
panels.title: Files Pinned

panels.description: Displays how many times the mount operation has been called (including failed invocations)

panels.description: Displays the current number of freed files in Alluxio
panels.title: Files Freed

panels.description: Displays how many times the unmount operation has been called
